Soulful House Sessions brings you an incredible selection of brand new soulful house samples direct from Andy Lee at Slipstreem Studios. Inspiration comes from the DJ`s and Clubs round the world dedicated to the finest in soulful and funky house grooves. Artists such as Masters At Work, Copyright, Jamie Lewis, Joey Negro, Micheal Watford, Kerri Chandler, Mr V and Miguel. Legendry labels such as King Street, NRK, Naked, Wave, Refunkt, Soufuric and SUSU to name a few have provided the musical back drop against which this CD positions its style and feel.
